data.description: Stunning, 3BED/2BA home in the highly sought-after Craft Farms North community! This home holds many value-enhancing features & upgrades including new luxury vinyl flooring in living areas, new carpet flooring in bedrooms, beautiful granite countertops throughout, all conveying appliances, automatic double garage, and more!! Upon entering the split bedroom plan home, a formal dining room is on the right, while the kitchen is on the left. The kitchen also holds another dining space and breakfast bar along with stainless steel appliances, pantry, and access to double garage via laundry room (holding conveying washer & dryer). The living room boasts a high, trey ceiling and splits the primary suite from the other 2 bedrooms & bathroom w/ tub/shower combo. The primary suite holds a high, trey ceiling, as well, along with a granite double vanity, garden tub, separate shower, walk-in closet, and separate water closet. Head out to the back covered patio w/ ceiling fan overlooking luscious backyard. Don't miss the opportunity to make this cozy home yours! Motto Mortgage Gulf Coast offering a free appraisal credit at closing, contact Kelly Hobbs for more information and to get Prequalified (251-968-3601).
